    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and slice (don't chop!) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>tortelloni </strong>for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have softened, drain your <strong>jumbo prawns</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained jumbo prawns</strong>, <strong>sliced garlic</strong> and your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 6-7 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are cooked, add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>drained</strong> <strong>tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chopped parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) to the pan</p><p>Give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce \u2013 this is your <strong>chilli, garlic & tomato jumbo prawns with tomato & mozzarella tortelloni</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/jumbo-chilli-prawns-with-tomato-and-mozzarella-tortelloni/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chilli & tomato jumbo prawns with tomato & mozzarella tortelloni </strong>topped with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
